title: Naga Chaitanya-Samantha remark: BJP slams Telangana govt, calls it 'utter disaster'
title_detail: {'type': 'text/plain', 'language': 'en-IN', 'base': 'https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/rssfeeds/-2128816011.cms', 'value': "Naga Chaitanya-Samantha remark: BJP slams Telangana govt, calls it 'utter disaster'"}
summary: BJP spokesperson Rachna Reddy criticizes the Congress-led Telangana government following Minister Konda Surekha's comments linking actors Naga Chaitanya and Samantha Ruth Prabhu's divorce to BRS leader KT Rama Rao.
